<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="intro-split">
      <div class="intro-split__body reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Life Beyond the Campus</span>
        <h2>The best of Atlanta and Fayette County, right outside our door.</h2>
        <p class="lead">Azalea Estates sits in one of the most enviable locations in the metro Atlanta area. Residents who want to get out and explore have no shortage of options, and those who prefer to stay in are just as well entertained.</p>
        <p>Our transportation program and Activity Director coordinate day trips and evening outings throughout the year: Fox Theatre productions, concerts, Atlanta Botanical Gardens, Braves games at Truist Park, and cultural events across greater Atlanta. Closer to home, we take full advantage of everything Fayetteville and Peachtree City have to offer, from local restaurants and events to seasonal festivals.</p>
        <p>And when there&rsquo;s no reason to leave, there&rsquo;s still every reason to celebrate. Our Activity Director and team can transform our common areas into a haunted mansion for Halloween, a gorgeous ballroom for the Valentine&rsquo;s dance, or whatever the occasion calls for. The energy and creativity on this campus are something families notice on their very first visit.</p>
        <p>We also bring the outside world in through a regular series of educational seminars, with knowledgeable guest speakers covering everything from local Fayetteville happenings to national and world affairs, because staying curious is part of living well.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-split__media reveal">
        <img src="{{ images.residentsLaughing }}" alt="Residents enjoying a festive community event at Azalea Estates" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="amenities-grid" style="margin-top: var(--space-8);">
      <div class="amenity-chip reveal">
        <div class="amenity-chip__icon">{{ icon('car', 22) }}</div>
        <div><h4>Greater Atlanta Outings</h4><p>Fox Theatre, Atlanta Botanical Gardens, Truist Park, concerts, and cultural events throughout the metro area.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="amenity-chip reveal">
        <div class="amenity-chip__icon">{{ icon('leaf', 22) }}</div>
        <div><h4>Local Fayette County Events</h4><p>Day trips and evenings out in Fayetteville and Peachtree City, including local dining, festivals, and community events.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="amenity-chip reveal">
        <div class="amenity-chip__icon">{{ icon('users', 22) }}</div>
        <div><h4>Themed Campus Events</h4><p>Our Activity Director transforms common areas for holidays and special occasions: Halloween, Valentine&rsquo;s, seasonal celebrations, and more.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="amenity-chip reveal">
